    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><br><br><h5> This article is reformatted from originally published at <a href="https://betterprogramming.pub/a-computer-science-students-perspective-on-undergraduate-research-275403933ef8"><strong>TDS(Towards Data Science)</strong></a></h5></br><h5> <a href="https://medium.com/@mary.paskhaver?source=post_page-----275403933ef8--------------------------------">Author : Mary Paskhaver</a> </h5></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content4 cid-tt5SM2WLsM" id="content4-2" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row justify-content-center">
                    <div class="title col-md-12 col-lg-9">
                        <h3 class="mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-4 display-2">
                            <strong>A Computer Science Student’s Perspective on Undergraduate Research</h3></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><h4 class="mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-4 display-5 text-muted">It can help you grow. But in what directions?</h4></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="image3 cid-tt612oXwA9" id="image3-5" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
