                <div class="image-wrapper"><div class="image_style" style="width:96%;"><picture><source sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" srcset="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/format:webp/1*Pc2qg-MX8TdES04H3N0NNQ.jpeg 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/format:webp/1*Pc2qg-MX8TdES04H3N0NNQ.jpeg 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/format:webp/1*Pc2qg-MX8TdES04H3N0NNQ.jpeg 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/format:webp/1*Pc2qg-MX8TdES04H3N0NNQ.jpeg 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/format:webp/1*Pc2qg-MX8TdES04H3N0NNQ.jpeg 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/format:webp/1*Pc2qg-MX8TdES04H3N0NNQ.jpeg 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/format:webp/1*Pc2qg-MX8TdES04H3N0NNQ.jpeg 1400w" type="image/webp"/><source data-testid="og" sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" srcset="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/1*Pc2qg-MX8TdES04H3N0NNQ.jpeg 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/1*Pc2qg-MX8TdES04H3N0NNQ.jpeg 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/1*Pc2qg-MX8TdES04H3N0NNQ.jpeg 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/1*Pc2qg-MX8TdES04H3N0NNQ.jpeg 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/1*Pc2qg-MX8TdES04H3N0NNQ.jpeg 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/1*Pc2qg-MX8TdES04H3N0NNQ.jpeg 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/1*Pc2qg-MX8TdES04H3N0NNQ.jpeg 1400w"/><img alt="" loading="lazy" role="presentation" src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:700/1*Pc2qg-MX8TdES04H3N0NNQ.jpeg"></picture></div><p class="mbr-description mbr-fonts-style mt-2 align-center display-12 text-muted" style="font-size:12px;">Photo by <a href="https://unsplash.com/ja/@kyledarrenhanson?utm_source=unsplash&utm_medium=referral&utm_content=creditCopyText" target="_self">Kyle Hanson</a> on <a href="https://unsplash.com/photos/1pyqUh8Jx3E?utm_source=unsplash&utm_medium=referral&utm_content=creditCopyText" target="_self">Unsplash</a>.</p><br></div></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Research. It sounds cool. It leads to amazing discoveries. It gets people noticed. And it’s not right for everyone.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">I decided to research with a professor this semester. Currently, I’m studying how to split videos into topics based on their transcripts. It’s an intensive process, and I often feel I’m bogged down or missing things. But I’m learning Python and exploring natural language processing.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Should you do research? Will research make you a better programmer? That depends. Let me describe my research experiences. That can help you make your decision.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><h4 class="mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-4 display-5">Research Means Lots of Learning</h4></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">I knew this when I started my project but didn’t internalize it.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Research isn’t just thinking of an idea and implementing it. It’s also not just about reading articles. You need to figure out how things work.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">For my project, I needed to do natural language processing in Python. I learned that to analyze a document, you need to do the following:</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><ul><li class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Preprocess it. For example, remove common words from it.</li><li class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Figure out how to represent the meanings of words mathematically. You can do this with word vectors.</li><li class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Extract meaning from these vectors and other data. Analyze it and use it to solve a problem.</li></ul></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">The last part continues to be difficult for me. I don’t always know if I’m looking for the right things in the right ways.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">For example, a few weeks ago, my professor and I started analyzing the cosine similarity of sentences to group them into topics.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">At first, I tried clustering sentences with high cosine similarities in a graph. Then, my professor suggested using latent semantic analysis with matrices instead. Uh oh. I’d already forgotten most of my linear algebra.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">But that motivated me to learn more about data analysis. I explored <a href="https://pandas.pydata.org/" target="_self">pandas</a> and <a href="https://scikit-learn.org/stable/index.html" target="_self">scikit-learn</a>, which I think is useful. And I gained a new appreciation for Python and how code can help us understand how we talk.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">So, research can be nerve-wracking. But it can motivate you to learn.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><h4 class="mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-4 display-5">Research Means Responsibility</h4></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Part of the reason I chose to research was that it would get me elective credit for my degree. Since I signed up for an asynchronous research class, I assumed I could finish my work early each week, then chill.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">That wasn’t always the case.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Some weeks, I could figure out a problem in a few hours. I could present what I’d done to my professor, and he would be pleased.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Other weeks, I’d struggle to finish certain tasks. During a call with my professor, I’d start discussing my strategies and be told to try something I’d never heard of. I’d leave these meetings confused, but I was too nervous to ask for help. Wasn’t I supposed to be learning by myself?</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">My fear pushed me to try new things. I read tutorials about topical segmentation and tried to understand them. I paced around my dorm and wrote down strategies I hadn’t tried yet.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">I became fixated on having something new to show my professor every time we met. In a way, this made me more responsible. Each time I left a meeting confused but had something to show a week later, I got proof I was more capable.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">But this fixation is tiring. Even now, while I write this, I worry I’m wasting time I could be spending on my project.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><h4 class="mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-4 display-5">Conclusion</h4></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Whether you should do research depends on your wants and goals. Ask yourself:</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><ul><li class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Will research help you learn skills you want to learn?</li><li class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Do you want to commit a lot of time to a project?</li><li class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Do you want to accept a lot of responsibility?</li></ul></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">It’s nice to imagine that research will make you an expert in a hot topic like machine learning. But becoming an expert is difficult. It’s not a linear process.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">My research experiences have not been incredible. But they haven’t sucked, either. I’m glad that I’m learning. I’m happy I can meet with a professor one-on-one.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">If you’re looking for those things, try research. If not, don’t worry. We all discover things in different ways.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Thanks for reading. Have a great day.</p></div></div></div></section><?php include_once 'Elemental/footer.php'; ?>